theorem Topology.P3_iff_interior_closure_eq_of_isClosed
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} (hA : IsClosed A) :
    Topology.P3 A ↔ interior (closure A) = A := by
  constructor
  · intro hP3
    exact Topology.interior_closure_eq_of_isClosed_of_P3 (A := A) hA hP3
  · intro hEq
    dsimp [Topology.P3]
    intro x hx
    have : x ∈ interior (closure A) := by
      simpa [hEq] using hx
    exact this
